Now you can clearly see that the values of each original row has been transposed to the corresponding BINGO column, so that values between 1-15 are in the first column (B), 16-30 under the second column (I), 31-45 under the third (N), 46-60 under the fourth (G), and 61-75 under the fifth (O).

